The paper also mentions the use of neural networks for classification, which is relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the assumptions made in deep learning, which is relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
